OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScargill marks 40th        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fanniversary of miners'     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstrike                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former miners' leader Arthur Scargill  
OL,6, was the guest of honour at a rally     
OL,7, marking 40 years since the year-long   
OL,8, strikes.                               
OL,10,FMr Scargill was involved in major      
OL,11,Findustrial action to prevent pit       
OL,12,Fclosures in Yorkshire and the rest of  
OL,13,Fthe UK in the mid-1980s.               
OL,15,FHe gave a 40-minute speech at Dodworth 
OL,16,FMiners Welfare near Barnsley at a rally
OL,17,Fmarking 40 years since the strikes.    
OL,19,FHe told the BBC the lesson for trade   
OL,20,Funionists was to "fight like we did".  
